trans-unit.source: Specifies which properties should be reported by type descriptors, specifically the <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor.GetProperties*> method.
trans-unit.target: Anger vilka egenskaper som ska rapporteras av typbeskrivningar, särskilt de <xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor.GetProperties*>metod.</xref:System.ComponentModel.TypeDescriptor.GetProperties*>

trans-unit.source: The PropertyFilterAttribute [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)] supports an internal mechanism that limits the number of properties on a type that are returned by the custom <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject> type descriptor.
trans-unit.target: PropertyFilterAttribute [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)] har stöd för en intern mekanism som begränsar antalet egenskaper i en typ som returneras av anpassat <xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject>skriver säkerhetsbeskrivning.</xref:System.Windows.DependencyObject>

trans-unit.source: If the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)] is found, the type descriptor narrows the scope of returned properties.
trans-unit.target: Om den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)] finns, typen descriptor begränsas omfånget för egenskaperna som returneras.

trans-unit.source: PropertyFilterAttribute differs from typical [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr#plural](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattrsharpplural-md.md)] because you cannot apply it to a class as metadata.
trans-unit.target: PropertyFilterAttribute skiljer sig från vanliga [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr#plural](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattrsharpplural-md.md)] eftersom du inte kan använda den för en klass som metadata.

trans-unit.source: The filter mechanism works through code instead of through static metadata.
trans-unit.target: Filterfunktionen fungerar via kod i stället för via statiska metadata.

trans-unit.source: Initializes a new instance of the <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"></xref> class.
trans-unit.target: Initierar en ny instans av den <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"> </xref> klass.

trans-unit.source: The options that describe this property filter.
trans-unit.target: De alternativ som beskrivs filtret.

trans-unit.source: This member supports the [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewk](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewk-md.md)] infrastructure and is not intended to be used directly from your code.
trans-unit.target: Den här medlemmen stöder den [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewk](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewk-md.md)] infrastrukturen och är inte avsedd att användas direkt från din kod.

trans-unit.source: To be added.
trans-unit.target: Som ska läggas till.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value that indicates whether the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"></xref> [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)] is equal to a specified object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar ett värde som anger om aktuellt <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"> </xref> [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)] är lika med ett angivet-objekt.

trans-unit.source: This implementation compares the <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions> values on each <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute> for value equality.
trans-unit.target: Den här implementeringen jämför de <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions>värdena på varje <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute>värdet likheten.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute> </xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions>

trans-unit.source: If the <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions> are the same, then the two <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute> instances are equal.
trans-unit.target: Om den <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions>är samma, sedan två <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute>instanserna är lika.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute> </xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions>

trans-unit.source: The object to compare to this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Objekt för att jämföra till den här <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if the specified <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"></xref> is equal to the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"></xref>; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om den angivna <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"> </xref> är lika med aktuellt <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"> </xref>, annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: Gets the filter options for this <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"></xref> [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Hämtar filteralternativ för den här <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"> </xref> [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: The value of Filter is the same value as was provided for the `filter` constructor argument when this <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute> was constructed.
trans-unit.target: Värdet för Filter är samma värde som angavs för den `filter` konstruktorargument när detta <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute>konstruerades.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute>

trans-unit.source: There is no other means of setting the Filter value.
trans-unit.target: Det finns inga andra sätt att ange filtervärdet.

trans-unit.source: The property filter options.
trans-unit.target: Egenskapen filteralternativ.

trans-unit.source: Returns the hash code for the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"></xref> [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)].
trans-unit.target: Returnerar hash-koden för aktuellt <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"> </xref> [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)].

trans-unit.source: A signed 32-bit integer value.
trans-unit.target: Ett signerat 32-bitars heltalsvärde.

trans-unit.source: Returns a value that indicates whether the property filter options of the current <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"></xref> [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)] match the property filter options of the provided object.
trans-unit.target: Returnerar ett värde som anger om egenskapen filteralternativ aktuella <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"> </xref> [!INCLUDE[TLA#tla_netframewkattr](~/add/includes/tlasharptla-netframewkattr-md.md)] matchar filteralternativen egenskap för det angivna objektet.

trans-unit.source: For attributes that store flags, which is true for <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute>, a Match result may be different from an <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute.Equals%2A> result.
trans-unit.target: För attribut som lagrar flaggor som gäller för <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute>, matchning resultatet kan skilja sig från en <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute.Equals%2A>resultat.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute.Equals%2A> </xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute>

trans-unit.source: For example, a filter of <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions> matches a filter of <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions>, because <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions> is a merge of all filter values.
trans-unit.target: Till exempel ett filter för <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions>matchar ett filter för <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions>eftersom <xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions>är en sammanslagning av alla filtervärden.</xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions> </xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions> </xref:System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterOptions>

trans-unit.source: The object to compare.
trans-unit.target: Objektet som ska jämföras.

trans-unit.source: This object is expected to be a <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"></xref>.
trans-unit.target: Det här objektet förväntas vara en <xref href="System.ComponentModel.PropertyFilterAttribute"> </xref>.

trans-unit.source: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref> if a match exists; otherwise, <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""></xref>.
trans-unit.target: <xref uid="langword_csharp_true" name="true" href=""></xref>Om det finns en matchning. Annars <xref uid="langword_csharp_false" name="false" href=""> </xref>.
